Business Rules:
BR1: Each tour must have at least one event.
BR2: Tours must have a valid start and end date.
BR3: Tours cannot be deleted if they have active bookings.
System Requirements:
SYSREQ1: Create a foreign key relationship to ensure tours are linked to at least one event in the database.
SYSREQ2: Add validation in the service layer to check that the start date is before the end date.
SYSREQ3: Implement a service-layer validation to prevent deletion of tours that have associated bookings.